    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能保护弱者免受地下兽人部队及其邪恶Boss的侵害吗？在脆弱的能源供给环上部署升级的高科技武器。精确调整塔的摆放和费用。环游世界的惊险旅程永无止境！</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与其他TD游戏不同的是环！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你失去了塔下的环，部署位置也会丢失。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235570/extras/527ce9d3178df2182ee01759ab65c873.poster.avif?t=1770158065\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235570/extras/527ce9d3178df2182ee01759ab65c873.webm?t=1770158065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235570/extras/527ce9d3178df2182ee01759ab65c873.mp4?t=1770158065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >定期更新！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是-个实时游戏，更新定期推出。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >漫长而充满惊喜的战役！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40 个各具特色的关卡，包含多种不同的环境。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7种多样化塔！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >机枪、火焰、坦克、医疗、银行、特斯拉和火箭</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3个升级等级。最后-次升级还会解锁塔的额外功能。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3种特殊武器！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >核弹、护盾、狙击手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235570/extras/3247f5da846bb3726166fdd7b43e60c2.poster.avif?t=1770158065\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235570/extras/3247f5da846bb3726166fdd7b43e60c2.webm?t=1770158065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235570/extras/3247f5da846bb3726166fdd7b43e60c2.mp4?t=1770158065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级塔和特殊武器！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据你的表现，你可以获得金币，用于战斗前升级武器。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10+敌人！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个世界的末尾都有强大的Boss。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧情</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟随故事了解更多关于Massive Defense宇宙的信息。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >离线游戏！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单人游戏，无需Wi-Fi。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽情享受吧！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏旨在成为顶尖塔防游戏。不断打磨和改进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目标是让你的时间物有所值，无多余填充 - 只有美味的游戏精华！</p>",
